headline: Agilent Refurbishment Centers Achieve Top-Level My Green Lab Certification
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., September 09, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that its Refurbishment Centers in Delaware, USA, and Singapore have achieved the highest level of My Green Lab Certification—Green level— an internationally recognized benchmark for laboratory sustainability.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell A and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 15.7% since March 2025, Agilent (currently trading at $128.85 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 5.7%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
